                    <span>If you practise Amerindian spirituality, Buddhism, Christianity, etc as your spiritual path; you wil find ways to set up an altar in your home.<P>My only minor nitpick is that in the Medicine Wheel layouts on pages 56-61. Ms Linn places the elements in the wrong directions IMHO.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Altars--Intentional living!</div>
